data.description: INCREDIBLE OPPORTUNITY! Call today to schedule your private showing of this 2021-BUILT HOME with 4 BEDROOMS, 2 BATHS, 2 CAR GARAGE, and OVER 2100 sq ft under air! Step inside and be greeted by a GENEROUS GREAT ROOM with VOLUME CEILINGS and EXPANSIVE SLIDERS that open to your screen enclosed lanai. The kitchen is a cook's delight with QUARTZ COUNTERTOPS, Whirlpool appliances, white shaker-style cabinetry with SOFT CLOSE DRAWERS & CABINETS, plus breakfast bar and pantry! Neutral, TILED FLOORS and 5 1/4 baseboards throughout the entire home! Primary suite is SPACIOUS and boasts walk-in closet, QUARTZ VANITY with an abundance of counter space, drawers & cabinets, plus a gorgeous walk-in shower. A SPLIT PLAN, you'll love the privacy of your new home! Guest rooms are conveniently located down a separate hall, with the guest bath in the center. Perfect for a growing family or extended stay-guests, the guest bath also offers a dual sinks, ample cabinet/drawer space, plus combo tub/shower. Inside utility room offers Samsung washer/dryer plus utility sink! Located on a quiet street with similarly well-cared for homes, you'll love the location! NO FLOOD INSURANCE REQUIRED! Close to I-75 and Palm Beach Blvd, with easy access to all that SW Florida has to offer! An easy drive to Top Golf, the Shops at the Forum, Buckingham Community Park, downtown Fort Myers River District, and so much more! WHY WAIT FOR A NEW BUILD - this 2021-BUILT HOME looks and feels like new! At this price, it's TIME TO MOVE!
